file.name: binary3.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.2
info:
  title: Title
  description: >
    Description
  version: 1.0.0
servers:
  - url: /api/v1
paths:
  /path:
    post:
      description: >
        Description
      operationId: operationId
      requestBody:
        required: true
        content:
          application/octet-stream:
            schema:
              type: string
              format: binary
      responses:
        '200':
          description:
            description
          content:
            application/octet-stream:
              schema:
                type: string
                format: binary
                x-scala-type: fs2.Stream[F, Byte]
        '400':
          description: 400 - The request was malformed or missing a required field.
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object
                description: Optional information about how the request was bad.
                properties:
                  fieldName:
                    type: string
                    description: >-
                      If this error was due to a particular field, this is the name of that field.
